环球音乐集团通过音乐健康联盟启动新的心理健康基金https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-group-launches-new-mental-health-fund-with-music-health-alliance-3837911?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=universal-music-团体发射新的 - 预选资金，拥有音乐保险Surej SinghFri, 14 Feb 2025 04:18:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsLet’s Talk – mental healthPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3837911 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是在查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）要求音乐行业在格莱美奖上更好地照顾艺术家之后</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-group-launches-new-mental-health-fund-with-music-health-alliance-3837911">Universal Music Group通过音乐健康联盟启动了新的心理健康基金，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/universal-music-group">环球音乐集团</a>宣布与音乐健康联盟合作启动新的音乐健康基金 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">在封面上 - 查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）：流行超新星，感觉就像是“拖拉比赛”的女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（2月13日），环球音乐集团（Universal Music Group）透露了<a href="https://www.universalmusic.com/universal-music-group-and-music-health-alliance-launch-music-industry-mental-health-fund/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">音乐行业心理健康基金</a>，该基金将为美国的现任和前音乐专业人士提供心理健康服务，甚至与该品牌签约或连接的人。</p><p>该合作伙伴关系通过对心理健康顾问的个性化建议，在必要时取消成本和资助资源建议的赠款，以确保通过额外的财务和心理健康支持来确保继续护理，以抵消成本和资助资源建议。</p><p>除了通过音乐行业心理健康基金提供的服务外，MHA还提供牙科护理资源，个人和家庭健康保险，高级护理支持，视力护理资源等。</p><p> UMG和MHA过去曾为“近1,000名客户服务，并为他们节省了超过1250万美元的医疗保健费用”  - <a href="https://www.universalmusic.com/universal-music-group-and-music-health-alliance-launch-music-industry-mental-health-fund/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">有关音乐行业心理健康基金的更多信息，请访问此处</a>。</p><p>目前尚不清楚该基金是否会扩展到包括世界各地的专业人士。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGBvny5zlkM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; h