在可能的地方获得快乐！”</p><p>这首歌的包含戴皇后肉丸是在泰勒的蛋糕上锦上添花的：“我已经写了这首歌，然后几个月后，我有史以来最喜欢的皇后肉丸在她的播客<em>马虎的秒数</em>上说的几乎一样，我知道必须制作专辑！”</p><p>自尊心将于4月25日通过Polydor发布12轨唱片“复杂的女人”  -<a href="https://selfesteem.lnk.to/AComplicatedWoman" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预订副本</a>。她已经预览了2021年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">Mercury</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">Brit</a>主题的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/self-esteem-prioritise-pleasure-review-3069775#:~:text=Assured%20and%20unapologetic%2C%20it's%20charged,laugh%20at%20the%20sheer%20absurdity">“优先享乐”</a>的后续行动，并在上个月发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/self-esteem-declares-i-deserve-to-be-here-on-focus-is-power-from-new-album-a-complicated-woman-3830836">“ Focus Is Is Power”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832519" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832519" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832519" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement.jpg" alt="自尊出版照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/SelfEsteemACompliatedWomanLive-show-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832519" class="wp-caption-text">自尊。学分：Scarlett Carlos Clarke</figcaption></figure><p>根据新闻稿，自尊的“复杂的女人”专辑旨在夺回对自己的生活的控制